The following radar control programs are intercompatible with
one another for dual-channel operation:

- normalscan       [*]
- pcodescan        [*]
- interleavescan
- rbspscan
- onebeamscan
- normalsound_usrp
- noopscan         [-]

[*] Note that normalscan and pcodescan are not compatible with
    one another; however, both control programs are compatible
    with any other mode in the list above.

[-] noopscan is used to turn off a channel for a specified
    period of time, and does not produce any data.
